text.tspan: Brickbase does something very simple, that yet cannot be found on international markets:
REITs a nd real estate funds are pools of properties, spread across a country or across the globe, and very often the investment product is not even real estate!

text.data-name: Liquidity is not an attribute that appeals only to investors an
text.tspan: Liquidity is not an attribute that appeals only to investors and financial practitioners: greater liquidity means cheaper cost of funding for property development projects. Greater liquidity in the real estate market would also have a tempering effect on the credit crunch that comes with periods of financial crisis

text.data-name: While investing in the shareholders' capital of a company can b
text.tspan: While investing in the shareholders' capital of a company can be done through a simple "Buy" order on a stock exchange, investing in real estate is a much more bureaucratic process.
Brickbase deconstructs the sales and purchase of real estate into a seamless process. Less bureaucracy, more investment.
